Chile Plane Crash Killed All 21 Onboard

-- B y   A l e x a n d e r   E m e r y
-- 
2011-09-04T00:44:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-04/chile-plane-crash-killed-all-21-onboard-defense-minister-allamand-says.html
All 21 people on board a Chilean
military plane that crashed off an island in the South  Pacific
Ocean  were killed, Defense Minister Andres Allamand said. The
minister, who flew over the crash site, said all onboard were
killed instantly. The plane was carrying businessmen, troops and
journalists when it crashed yesterday.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alexander Emery in  Lima  at 
